commit_message: Change more integer variables from 16 to 32 bits
Fix help message + int16 -> int32 in polynomial solver
Subset samples based on VMR for CN analysis
`parascopy cn`: Pool reads to BAM by default
Use multiple pooled files for parascopy `cn` and `call`
Pool reads into multiple output files
Add new arg flag for testing
Add more padding to pooled reads. Improves precision
Allow for non-reference sample in the EM-algorithm
Validate pooled BAM file read groups
Add option to provide --reliable-threshold in case of cn-using
Move test pipeline into a separate file
Fix a bug in table construction
Output PSV read counts and genotypes to vcf file
